title: Dr. Gaurav Nagpal: Successfully Leading Amazing Tech Programs with Passion and Devotion - Analytics Insight
content: Dr. Gaurav Nagpal: Successfully Leading Amazing Tech Programs with Passion and Devotion  Analytics Insight
description: Dr. Gaurav Nagpal is the Faculty of Decision Sciences, Analytics and Operations at BITS Pilani. He visualizes the collaboration of WILP with the industry to become deeper and even more strategic in the future.
